thread.title_full: Ace Jewelers Beoordeeld door Frank S.

author: Frank S.
title: Frank S.
text: My buying experience from Ace Jewelers was exemplary. From the ease of ordering my IWC straps and buckles to the meticulous packaging and fast shipping to NJ, Ace Jewelers does it right. Excellent communication and follow up as well from their personnel (Jenna). I will be a repeat customer for sure!
